"{\n  \"text\": \"Hey everybody, Scotty here out in Neadville, Texas, at our Regenerative Agriculture project. This is our flat pile. What we've been doing is we've been putting all of our compostable material into a flat pile because we don't have a tractor, and then uh we rent a tractor uh from a neighbor, and the neighbor as well because he drives the tractor on Sundays when he can come over, and he proceeds to put this pile onto these aerated static pipes, which will blow oxygen into them as they uh use up the oxygen because that's one of the limiting factors in a hot compost. So this is like just a little primary breakdown we do, but the real breakdown is going to go on these pipes. Unfortunately, it's been rainy out here, and we haven't had a chance to use the tractor in about three weeks, so this is kind of sitting on the ground becoming anaerobic. Not exactly what you want to do, but we're gonna be working on it. Thanks, y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hey everybody, Scotty here out in Neadville, Texas, at our Regenerative Agriculture project.\",\n      \"start\": 0.32,\n      \"end\": 5.52,\n      \"duration\": 5.2,\n      \"confidence\": 0.981,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" He\",\n          \"start\": 0.32,\n          \"end\": 0.56,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 0.951\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"y\",\n          \"start\": 0.56,\n          \"end\": 0.64,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 0.999\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 0.72,\n          \"end\": 0.8,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 0.8,\n          \"end\": 0.88,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"ody\",\n          \"start\": 0.88,\n          \"end\": 0.96,\n        